      "text": "test.discover tests in \u0027_fixtures_sensitive\u0027, pattern=\u0027*.fixture.goal\u0027, recursive, write to %tests%",
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "Companion to TestReportMasksSensitiveVariables \u2014 same fixture, but with\nformat=\u0027junit\u0027 so the committed junit.xml snapshot can be eyeballed.\nProves the JUnit XML path also masks [Sensitive] PrivateKey \u2014 BuildJUnit\nemits run.Error?.Message directly, so AssertionError.Message itself must\nbe sanitised (not just the structured JSON envelope).",
